      <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>To the extent permitted by law, KingWorX's total liability to you for any claim arising from your use of our Site or products is limited to the purchase price paid for the specific product giving rise to the claim.</p>
      <p>We are not liable for:</p>
