    <section id="t10" class="policy-section">
      <h2>10. Dispute Resolution</h2>
      <p>If you have a complaint, please contact us first at <a href="mailto:support@kingworx.com.au">support@kingworx.com.au</a>. We are committed to resolving disputes fairly and promptly.</p>
      <p>If we cannot resolve your complaint, you may refer the matter to the relevant consumer protection authority in your state or territory, or to the Australian Competition and Consumer Commission (ACCC).</p>
